songs.title: I WILL NEVER CHANGE
songs.lyrics:
Do you think I'm going to change?
I am as I want, I am as if they taught me
Everyone looks at me like a parasite
Maybe it's true, maybe it's a nuisance

But that admits it does not mean it will stop being that way
My way of thinking is different from yours? that argument can be ...
I want to be different from you, but I will not change, I will never be different
17, 21, is what is repeated, is what I look, is what I hallucinate
My verses are generic? Are they the same as the pile? they are not

They are very different from my idols, they are different from my life
They are all generic, I still remember the stupid boy who wanted to be a policeman
I always had this in mind
